msgid "I will not say if this is a good decision, but I will follow you."
msgstr "Non vi diro' che e' una saggia decisione, ma vi seguiro'."

#: data/scenarios/Eastern_Invasion/Undead_Border_Patrol.cfg:141
#, fuzzy
