#: data/scenarios/Eastern_Invasion/Undead_Border_Patrol.cfg:189
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Noo!!! He will reach Mal-Ravanal's capital, and I shall be punished for "
"letting him escape!"
msgstr ""
"Noo!!! Raggiungera' la capitale di Mal-Ravanal e saro' punito per averli "
"fatti fuggire!"

