"\n"
"Victory:\n"
"@Survive the night\n"
"Defeat:\n"
"#Death of Gweddry\n"
"#Death of Dacyn\n"
"#Death of Owaec\n"
"#Death of Sudoc\n"
"#Death of Konrad"
